snippet: Justin Tucker kicked his sixth field goal of the game with 38 seconds left, and Baltimore came back to beat Detroit, securing the A.F.C. wild-card spot with the win.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Baltimore Ravens beat Detroit Lions, 18-16; victory eliminates New York Jets from playoff race; other news noted.
lead_paragraph: Justin Tucker kicked his sixth field goal of the game with 38 seconds left, and Baltimore came back to beat Detroit, securing the A.F.C. wild-card spot with the win.

headline.main: 61-Yard Kick Lifts Ravens and Finishes Jets
headline.print_headline: 61-Yard Kick Lifts Ravens and Finishes Jets
